com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium

Class Notification

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.Notification

  • public final class Notification
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents object that contains information about browser notification, stores notification state data and provides functionality that allows user to perform operations with notification (click, closeInternal, etc.) and listen browser events associated with this notification instance.

    If some browser instance has been disposed or reloaded than all notifications that were created in the scope of this browser instance context would be marked as closed and all notification event listeners associated with this notification would be informed about it.

    表示一个对象，该对象包含有关浏览器通知的信息，存储通知状态数据，并提供允许用户执行带有通知的操作（单击，closeInternal等）并侦听与此通知实例关联的浏览器事件的功能。如果某个浏览器实例已被处置或重新加载，则在该浏览器实例上下文范围内创建的所有通知都将被标记为已关闭，并且将通知所有与此通知关联的通知事件侦听器。

      • isClosed

        public boolean isClosed()
        Informs about the state of the notification. Closed notification will not receive and proceed events from browser and will do nothing on public method invocations. Notification can be closed by user invoking the close() method or via JavaScript code Notification.close().
        通知有关通知状态的信息。已关闭的通知将不会从浏览器接收并继续处理事件，并且不会对公共方法调用执行任何操作。可以通过用户调用close（）方法或通过JavaScript代码Notification.close（）关闭通知。
        Returns:
        true if this notification is closed. 如果此通知已关闭。

      • removeNotificationListener

        从注册的通知侦听器列表中删除通知侦听器。如果未注册该侦听器，则不执行任何操作
        Parameters:

      • close

        public void close()
        Informs browser that this notification was closed by user and marks it as closed. See isClosed() Does nothing if this notification has been already closed or if browser instance in which context this notification was created has been disposed or reloaded.
        通知浏览器该通知已被用户关闭，并将其标记为已关闭。请参见isClosed（）如果此通知已被关闭或在此上下文中创建了该通知的浏览器实例已被释放或重新加载，则不执行任何操作。
